    2707 XSORT Reads and sorts Bulk Data Section Main Index Remarks: 1.XSORT does not stop on error detection; therefore, the following statement should appear after the module: IF (NOGOXSRT) EXIT $ 2.If BULKOLD is purged or empty, then the current Bulk Data is sorted and copied into BULK. 3.XSORT must be specified after the IFP1 module.
